# SaralAI: Complete Analysis & Perfection Plan

## 🔍 What I Found (Thinking Like a Real User)

I went through **every single file** in the codebase. Here is the honest picture of what works, what is broken, and what is missing — evaluated as a real Gujarati/Hindi-speaking rural user would experience it.

